  "original_query": "[Chat History Summary] The conversation involved retrieving information about the most recent borrower and then determining how many loan accounts that borrower has. [Current Question] Хамгийн өндөр олголттой зээлийн дансны мэдээлэл?",
  "tables_count": 0,
  "tables_selected": [],
  "names_extracted_count": 20,
  "query_complexity": "SIMPLE",
  "was_decomposed": true,
  "final_sql": "WITH latest_disbursed AS (     SELECT         acnt_code,         MAX(acnt_name) KEEP (DENSE_RANK LAST ORDER BY txn_date) AS acnt_name,         MAX(customer_name) KEEP (DENSE_RANK LAST ORDER BY txn_date) AS customer_name,         MAX(cur_code) KEEP (DENSE_RANK LAST ORDER BY txn_date) AS cur_code,         MAX(adv_date) KEEP (DENSE_RANK LAST ORDER BY txn_date) AS adv_date,         MAX(adv_amount) KEEP (DENSE_RANK LAST ORDER BY txn_date) AS original_adv_amount,         MAX(adv_amount * rate) KEEP (DENSE_RANK LAST ORDER BY txn_date) AS adv_amount_in_mnt,         MAX(status) KEEP (DENSE_RANK LAST ORDER BY txn_date) AS status     FROM dbm.loan_balance_detail     WHERE adv_amount IS NOT NULL       AND (acnt_name IS NOT NULL OR customer_name IS NOT NULL)     GROUP BY acnt_code     HAVING MAX(adv_amount) KEEP (DENSE_RANK LAST ORDER BY txn_date) > 0 ) SELECT     acnt_code,     acnt_name,     customer_name,     cur_code,     adv_date,     original_adv_amount,     adv_amount_in_mnt,     status FROM latest_disbursed ORDER BY adv_amount_in_mnt DESC FETCH FIRST 1 ROW ONLY;",
  "result_count": 1,
  "final_answer": "Таны хүсэлтийн дагуу хамгийн өндөр олголттой зээлийн дансны мэдээллийг хүргэж байна:  - Дансны код: 3600000127 - Дансны нэр: ЭРДЭНЭС ТАВАН ТОЛГОЙ ХК - Харилцагчийн нэр: ЭРДЭНЭС ТАВАНТОЛГОЙ ХК - Валют: ам.доллар - Олгосон огноо: 2012-10-05 - Олгосон дүн: 100,000,000 ам.доллар - Олгосон дүн (төгрөгөөр): 359,361,000,000 төгрөг - Статус: C"
